<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere in =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.=
mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33301955.257406/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2=
NvbnRlbnQvOTQ0MjJhMTYtNWU5Yy00ZjY3LWJiNjMtYzg4NzljMmRhNWM0/607f07ceef4b8524=
