<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When UBS Group AG acquired Credit Suisse Group=
 AG in March, Credit Suisse=E2=80=99s additional tier 1 capital securities =
were <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33301955.2574=
06/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMjAv=
